data.description: This 2.93 acre property offers a 3 bedroom, 2 bath private manufactured home. Cathedral ceilings and picture windows open and brighten the living space leading out to a 12 x 30 deck. The deck oversees a valley of pines.  The Master-Suite has two sinks and double shower doors. Outbuildings include a shed and carport. The yard is partially fenced which may be used for farm animals, a dog run or possibly a garden.
